data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of South Temecula's prestigious Redhawk community! Located on a corner lot in a quite cul-de-sac, this beautiful residence features 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms & a 3-car garage, providing a perfect blend of comfort and style. Nestled in a prime location, home to highly-ranked high school - Great Oak High and just walking distance from Jackson Helen Elementary school! This property is adjacent to Redhawk's 18-hole golf course, offering dramatic elevations, breathtaking views and a serene atmosphere. Situated for convenience, the property is a stone's throw from the 15 freeway, providing effortless access to nearby attractions such as the renowned Pechanga Resort and Casino. Embrace the allure of wine country living, with vineyards just moments away, while enjoying the convenience of proximity to upscale dining and premier shopping destinations. Don't miss the chance to own a piece of Temecula's luxury real estate. Immerse yourself in sophistication, schedule a viewing, and experience the epitome of refined living in this exclusive Redhawk residence. Your dream home awaits!
